Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:05.48,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,So Kaho, what do you say to going on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:07.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,A d-date?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:12.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Like I said the other day, I've always thought you were good looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:14.99,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.99,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't be dealing with this right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:21.00,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not currently wearing any underwear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:26.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:26.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Episode 6: I'm Going to be Found Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.69,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It could even be right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,We could just skip fifth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:36.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I think... we should probably just go to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:38.01,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.47,0:00:41.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You might think it's a waste of time now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,but when you think about the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.59,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You know, Kaho...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:48.53,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I was thinking this the other day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:49.94,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:51.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:55.99,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's like you're... more mature somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.45,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}T-This is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's a little suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:03.49,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You know what? I changed my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.49,0:01:05.75,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Let's skip class together!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:08.00,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:11.60,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Wait, where are we going, Aida?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:13.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Say, Kaho...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:15.29,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,...wanna do it with me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:17.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-What? "Again"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.79,0:01:22.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, it was just the day before \Nyesterday on my way home from work...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.15,0:01:24.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,We went to a hotel together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:26.31,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:27.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:31.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way, how long has Kaho been doing that kind of thing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:33.85,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:34.87,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I was just pulling your leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:35.53,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.21,0:01:37.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,But seriously, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:39.99,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you deny it just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.73,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I knew something seemed suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.73,0:01:47.92,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,If you don't tell me what it is, maybe I'll just do something even more lewd.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:55.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he gropes my butt, he'll know I'm not wearing panties!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:57.86,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't let that happen—I just can't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.88,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That's enough of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:04.49,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Dammit, Kanie again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:06.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I could say the same about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.59,0:02:08.56,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to address me properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:11.52,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}K-Kanie? How did you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:14.18,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I hope you understand how serious this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:17.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You could be suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:21.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think—there was just something I wanted to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:22.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:27.26,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,See you later, Kaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:32.96,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,U-Umm, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:34.42,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:36.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-Is he mad?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:39.47,Signs,,0,0,0,,AV Room
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.79,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What did you think you were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:46.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I, umm... Well, it's not like my cover's {\i1}completely{\i0} blown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.12,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:49.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:53.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Anyway, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.69,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:58.48,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. I little surprised, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:02.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I told you I'd protect you, then this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.41,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I-It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:08.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,As long as you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:15.37,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,S-So I've been wondering since the class reunion...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:17.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Kanie, do you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.87,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,D-Don't, Kanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Are you wet because of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.48,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.94,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Really? Is it because of me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:34.90,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.82,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,This is in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.18,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Don't cover them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.29,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:42.70,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Kanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:46.78,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:58.08,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No, no! Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.20,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Stop, what are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:12.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.96,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Not there, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.20,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:22.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:05:04.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted this reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:12.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:17.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:23.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:28.74,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:34.30,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:39.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:43.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:47.56,Songs,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:53.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,hidden deep within those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:58.26,Songs,,0,0,0,,I can't control these feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:05.42,Songs,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, my heart is being snatched away
